<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>核心竞争定位 - 千站液冷超充项目</title>
    <style>
        .tech-image-container {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.9);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 2px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .tech-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .image-caption {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--wm-info);
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../world-monitor-theme.css">
</head>
<body class="no-transition">
    <div class="wm-container">
    <header class="wm-header">
        <div class="wm-header-content">
            <a href="../index.html" class="wm-btn">← 返回首页</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="wm-main">
        <div class="wm-panel">
            <h1 style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 20px;">核心竞争定位</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 20px; color: var(--wm-text-secondary); max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">Core Competitive Positioning</p>
        </div>

        <section class="wm-panel">
            <h2>系统架构总览</h2>
            <div class="tech-image-container">
                <img src="images/系统架构图.png" alt="系统架构图" class="tech-image">
                <p class="image-caption">千站液冷超充项目系统架构图</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="wm-panel">
            <h2>三层系统架构</h2>
            <div class="service-detail">
                <h3>基础设施层</h3>
                <p>华为600kW全液冷超充设备、储能系统、电力配套设备</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail">
                <h3>平台服务层</h3>
                <p>智能调度平台、运营管理系统、数据分析平台</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail">
                <h3>应用服务层</h3>
                <p>用户端APP、运维端管理、数据可视化、支付结算</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="wm-panel">
            <h2>技术方案详解</h2>
            <div class="tech-image-container">
                <img src="images/充电站布局图.png" alt="充电站布局图" class="tech-image">
                <p class="image-caption">超充站布局设计图</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-image-container">
                <img src="images/液冷系统原理图.png" alt="液冷系统原理图" class="tech-image">
                <p class="image-caption">液冷系统工作原理</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-image-container">
                <img src="images/电力系统架构图.png" alt="电力系统架构图" class="tech-image">
                <p class="image-caption">电力系统架构设计</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="wm-panel">
            <h2>核心优势</h2>
            <div class="advantages-grid">
                <div class="advantage-item">
                    <h3>超快充电</h3>
                    <p>600kW最大功率，充电速度全球领先</p>
                </div>
                <div class="advantage-item">
                    <h3>液冷散热</h3>
                    <p>全液冷架构，设备寿命更长</p>
                </div>
                <div class="advantage-item">
                    <h3>智能运维</h3>
                    <p>AIoT技术，无人值守运营</p>
                </div>
                <div class="advantage-item">
                    <h3>绿色环保</h3>
                    <p>光储充一体，清洁能源</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        </main>
<footer style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 0; color: var(--wm-text-secondary); opacity: 0.7;">
            <p>© 2025 KeyTrader. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) entry.target.classList.add('visible');
            });
        }, {threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'});
        document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
    </script>
</body>
</html>
